<template>
    <sapn>
        <el-form :inline="true" :model="formInline" class="demo-form-inline">
            <el-form-item label="StudyInfoName">
                <el-input v-model="formInline.user" placeholder="StudyInfoName"></el-input>
            </el-form-item>
            <el-form-item label="StudyTypeName">
                <el-select v-model="studyTypeId" placeholder="Select">
                    <el-option
                        v-for="item in selectData"
                        :key="item.id"
                        :label="item.studyTypeName"
                        :value="item.id"
                    />
                </el-select>
            </el-form-item>
            <el-form-item>
                <el-button type="primary" @click="onSubmit">Query</el-button>
            </el-form-item>
        </el-form>
        <el-table :data="tableData" style="width: 100%">
            <el-table-column prop="StudyInfoName" label="StudyInfoName" />
            <el-table-column prop="StudyInfoDescribe" label="StudyInfoDescribe" />
            <el-table-column prop="StudyTypeName" label="StudyTypeName" />
            <el-table-column prop="CreateTime" label="CreateTime" />
            <el-table-column prop="UpdateTime" label="UpdateTime" />
        </el-table>
        <el-pagination small background layout="prev, pager, next" :total="50" class="mt-4"></el-pagination>
    </sapn>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import { defineComponent, reactive, ref } from 'vue'
import StudyInfoApi from '@/api/studyInfoApi'
export default defineComponent({
    setup() {
        const tableData: any = []
        let selectData: any = []


        StudyInfoApi.GetStudyType().then(result => {
            result.data.forEach( (item: { id: any }) => {
                selectData.push({
                    id: item.id
                })
            });

        })

        const studyTypeId: any = ref('');
        const formInline = reactive({
            user: '',
            region: '',

        })

        const onSubmit = () => {
            console.log('submit!')
        }
        return {
            studyTypeId,
            tableData,
            formInline,
            selectData,
            onSubmit
        }
    }
}
)

</script>
<style>
.el-pagination {
    float: right;
    margin-top: 10px;
}
</style>
